snippet.title: Life by You 'Jobs' Developer Presentation Trailer - Future Games Show Summer Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

Paradox Tectonic’s King Choi dropped by the Future Games Show Summer Showcase to deliver a developer presentation for Life by You, revealing exclusive footage of the barista job. Life by You is coming to Steam Early Access on September 12, 2023.

#FutureGamesShow #FGS
